headline: Qnity Electronics, Inc. to Host Business Update Webcast Call on Thursday, November 6, 2025 at 4:30pm ET
summary: WILMINGTON, DEL., October 27, 2025--Qnity Electronics, Inc. ("Qnity"), announced it will hold a business update webcast on Thursday, November 6, 2025, at 4:30 p.m. ET. This will follow the company’s planned separation from DuPont de Nemours, Inc. ("DuPont"), expected to be completed on November 1, 20251. Qnity is expected to be listed under the ticker "Q" on the NYSE.
